// Datalog Frames
//   A datalog frame has the following format and [size]
//
//  ModbusAddress		[1]
//  ModbusFunctionCode	[1]  
//	FrameNumber			[2]
//	DatalogRecord(0)	[4]
//	DatalogRecord(1)	[4]
//  ...
//	DatalogRecord(13)	[4]
//	ModbusCrc			[2]
//
//  Datalog Records
//   A datalog record has the following format and [size]
//
//	gasReading			[2]
//	temperature			[1]
//	status				[1]
